Technical leadership, build a team, build a culture, do media, do reports, meet sponsors, manage staff, tactical leadership, physical development, mental skills, sports science, manage injured players, develop strategic plans, comply with the rules and laws of the game, work 7 days a week in full view of the public, fans, media....and win or lose your job.
